snippet.title: Bingo64 for SM64: Version 0.0alpha Release
snippet.description:
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/cShWXHe
Download v0.6a: https://mega.nz/file/RgYmmJKC#yGt3WXYP824CD-H7Udfbr7y0KYbnbeNGpGwOARD8wKI

Controls: Press L to reveal Bingo board. Use the D-pad to move the cursor. You may have to change your graphics plugin on your emulator (I use GlideN64).

This is a ROM hack that genteelman and I made. Feel free to join our discord to report bugs and offer suggestions! Enjoy!

Old downloads, in case you want to relive the past:
v0.0a: https://mega.nz/#!w5YxiKyI!aWtZ-r-BxaOqcIN4LaXyWHsdMHl3ObQC9JBgLF_qxEQ)

v0.2a: https://mega.nz/#!Q0w2GKhI!NzOVLyBmoEh5_cdhLF6TsCLL_IuI2BOdguj9KeupBcU
v0.3a: https://mega.nz/#!FpRwiY4a!wI_JDf0tGek2BBm1EgcwPfJWBw69XGNnYD91A69m1nw
v0.4a: https://mega.nz/#!A4wXlIiK!ueFt7Bss0wIQ41dX-OSsGUuE4WjTLu8pEQiqtOjF1lc
